parameters:
Damn it! Those bitches! They've set the
place on fire!\n< Thief >

My precious hoarded treasure! Water! Put
out the fire!\n< Thief >

Yo... Finally showed up, huh? I've been
waiting...\n< ??? >
Huh? Isn't it just Erika alone?\n< Boss >

Well, that figures. You wouldn't dare do
this without some help.\n< Boss >
Eh? Erika-chan, you say!\n< Bear Claw Dodge >

So you called for help from your peers
with your pitiful screams, huh!\n< Bear Claw Dodge >

Did your rescuer get to see you crying
and wailing about how much you didn't
want it?\n< Bear Claw Dodge >

You were so against getting pregnant
with my kid, you even groveled on your
knees! But I shoved it in straight away!\n< Bear Claw Dodge >

The look on your face when my thick
semen was pouring into you! I wish I
could've shown that to your rescuer
too~?\n< Bear Claw Dodge >

Such worthless provocation. Not even
worth responding to.\n< Serena >

\n< Serena >There are five of them... and two of
us... Erika-dono, you can move, right?

I can't exactly fly or jump around, but
yeah.\n< Erika >

But, well... my insides are boiling like
lava right now...!\n< Erika >
I can't just collapse here...!\n< Erika >

I'll take my precious grenade... shove
it up that shithead's ass and light the
fuse!!\n< Erika >
Indeed! That's the spirit! Then...!\n< Serena >

You have insulted, mocked, tormented,
harassed, and toyed with my friend Erika
Rinruto!\n< Serena >

Such folly! Such evil deeds! They cannot
be overlooked! They cannot be forgiven!\n< Serena >

I stake my life and my honor! Today,
right here! I shall deliver a blow that
befits your actions!\n< Serena >
Hah? What kind of mumbo jumbo is that?\n< Bear Claw Dodge >

What's about to start here is the
slaughter show of you sow pigs!\n< Bear Claw Dodge >

I'll punch, slash, beat down, and break
you!\n< Bear Claw Dodge >

And fill your last moments with dick and
cum!\n< Bear Claw Dodge >
Did you see that, Serena?! I did it!\n< Erika >

How about that! You bastards! How about
that! ...Toying with... someone's...
body...! How dare you do whatever you
please...!\n< Erika >

I'll make you taste the pain and
suffering of being forcefully
penetrated...\n< Erika >

Heh... heh, I'm okay... I'm okay. Just
tripped over my feet a bit...\n< Erika >

But damn... even for me, this time I'm a
bit worn out...\n< Erika >

Talking about strategies and all that...
in the end, it turned into a frontal
assault.\n< Erika >

And in the end, I didn't even get to use
my trump card...\n< Erika >

I could still shove it in now if I
wanted to...\n< Erika >

It was a weapon prepared to defeat the
enemy monster. If it could be conserved,
isn't that a good thing?\n< Serena >

That's true too. It would be a waste to
use it on such trash... Ah, ouch ouch
ouch...!\n< Erika >
Can you walk to town...?\n< Serena >

If I use this guy as a cane, somehow...
But are you really okay, Serena...?\n< Erika >

The defense of Affabilis is still
intact. Fortunately, there are no major
injuries.\n< Serena >

But my whole body hurts... and I'm
tired... I'd like to refrain from such a
big fight for a while.\n< Serena >

Hah-hah, I'd like to decline such an
ordeal for good.\n< Erika >

...Alright, we can't dawdle too much.
Let's get going.\n< Erika >

We need to get out of here quick. The
smell of blood will attract stray dogs
and monsters.\n< Erika >

Indeed, this is not the time to take
things leisurely.\n< Serena >

After all, we're in no shape to even
handle a single puppy right now.\n< Serena >

Ah... then just one last thing, just a
little bit.\n< Erika >
Take THAT--!! Die in agony!!\n< Erika >

You bastards, UGH!! Human trash! Lower
than monsters, the lowest of the low
scum!\n< Erika >

To think you would...! To think you
would do as you please...! Do as you
please and rape someone!!\n< Erika >

You'll be left here to rot! Die! All of
you, just die!\n< Erika >

Bleed out and die! Burn in a fire and
die! Be devoured alive by monsters!\n< Erika >

Suffer! Writhe! Squirm! Die regretting
ever being born!!\n< Erika >

Ah... sorry... That was lame... But I
just couldn't... hold it in.\n< Erika >

Sniffle... Alright... let's go. We'll
leave the rest to the guild guys.\n< Erika >

Ah, let's just push all the troublesome
cleanup onto the Master.\n< Serena >
We have that much right.\n< Serena >

Eheheh, no kidding. While we're out here
struggling, they're just polishing
chairs with their asses—Serena!\n< Erika >

...Somehow I've managed to get this
close without being discovered.\n< Serena >

...The area is surrounded by cliffs, and
there are many lookouts at the entrance.
It seems we have no choice but to use
Erika-sama's rope to infiltrate...\n< Serena >
...A human corpse, is it? That is...\n< Serena >

To kill people, steal their valuables,
and not only that but to also desecrate
their bodies...! Damn thieves...!\n< Serena >

I must hurry, I cannot allow Erika-sama
to be laid out there with them.\n< Serena >
Infighting...? More like a lynching.\n< Serena >

No one's trying to stop it. On the
contrary, they're laughing... enjoying
it, that is.\n< Serena >

To think Erika-sama is captured by such
scoundrels...\n< Serena >

I must rescue her. Ah, I must rescue her
no matter what.\n< Serena >

The rope is said to be above the cliff.
Let's go.\n< Serena >
